Subject: {{{remoteUser.collective.name}}} added you as {{role}} to {{{collective.name}}} on Open Collective

{{> header}}

{{> toplogo}}

<p>{{> greeting}}</p>

<p>{{remoteUser.collective.name}} (cced) added you as {{role}} for <a href="https://opencollective.com/{{collective.slug}}">{{collective.name}}</a> on Open Collective.</p>

{{#if isAdmin }}
<p>As an administrator, you can <a href="{{config.host.website}}/dashboard/{{collective.slug}}">edit the settings</a> and add or remove team members.</p>
{{else}}
<p>You are now listed as a team member on <a href="https://opencollective.com/{{collective.slug}}">https://opencollective.com/{{collective.slug}}</a>.</p>
{{/if}}

<h2>Your details:</h2>

<table>
  {{#if recipient.collective.previewImage}}
    <tr><th>Avatar:</th><td><img src="{{recipient.collective.previewImage}}" height="64" /></td></tr>
  {{else}}
  <tr><th>Avatar:</th><td>No avatar</td></tr>
  {{/if}}
  <tr><th>Name:</th><td>{{recipient.collective.name}}</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Short description:</th><td>{{recipient.collective.description}}</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Website:</th><td>{{recipient.collective.website}}</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Twitter:</th><td>{{recipient.collective.twitterHandle}}</td></tr>
</table>

<p>If you have questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>

{{> footer}}
